connect20/whitesunrise_bongo_internation.name: connect20/WhiteSunrise_Bongo_International

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/whitesunrise_bongo_internation.description: Bongo International is a new international checkout process in which all orders enter Magento as a domestic shipment. This means that all merchants have to do is fulfill more domestic orders. No need for additional paperwork, compliance checks, or hassle.
